{"tid":1588751,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔認為有咁多汽油彈勇武","createTime":"2019-09-23T03:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T11:40:00.000Z","uid":173326,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"948287fb35379ca130473a07ad62002d9888733e","tid":1588751,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"經過3個月好多勇武都拉左，而且香港人主動攻擊嘅心理關口未突破。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係示威者暴力，太子狗屋咁多水馬圍住入口點會冇事？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>明顯掟嘅都係唔想傷到任何人，只想鏡頭面前俾人覺得示威者太暴力，想正當化黑警濫暴酷刑嘅罪行，確保藍絲堅定支持。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而且汽油彈呢類武器嘅製造、攜帶、使用都要冒好大風險，相信係黑警自製/大陸人運入嚟，掟嘅可能係休班狗/臥底狗/fucking幫等等想製造暴力觀感嘅有心人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果見到玩火/汽油彈，<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要唔傷自己人，就唔需要阻止</span></ins>，可能佢真係自己人。</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">但要留意小心附近有冇人攞伸縮棍出嚟，黑警隨時出嚟拉人屈佢放火。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"bc78467b8e091d1c26af922d2dd36a1c5e5bc453","tid":1588751,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"9876c6a8ff83c84c276556c050ad70f58c77e0ad","tid":1588751,"uid":77102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"鬼就一定有，捉就捉唔到，但一定要防範<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73C11Ov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73C11Ov.jpg&h=632a9756&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51f069d8059a38e600abb9026b18145b12f6a69c","tid":1588751,"uid":265739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:20:30.000Z","msg":"咁撚容易帶到出去咩<br />\n仲要大量"},{"pid":"f95148b3a5dec091910884e8dfeec67e8e9da109","tid":1588751,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quot